data.description: Welcome to 506 E 4th in the friendly town of Panhandle! This charming residence is the perfect match for first-time homebuyers or growing families seeking comfort and convenience. With 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this cozy house offers ample space for everyone. The expansive living area invites you to create lasting memories. Living area is open to the dining space which is ideal for family meals or entertaining guests. Retreat to the large, secluded primary suite, complete with a 3/4 bath, offering privacy and relaxation. The additional two bedrooms are well-sized and share a convenient full hall bathroom. Step outside to find not one, but two detached garages providing exceptional storage options or space for a hobbyist's workshop. Call this one home today!
